issue.title: Trim form input
issue.body:
On certain platforms, usually mobile, spaces are automatically inserted after typing/auto-completion. When I first tried using the visualizer I ran into this same issue!

To solve it, I remove any white space from either end of each key.

issue.title: Exclude directories
issue.body: Is there/could there be a way to exclude directories? Many golang projects have a `vendor/` directory that includes the source for all of their build dependencies (usually far larger than the rest of the project). For an example, checkout `hashicorp/consul`.

issue.title: Merge user/organization and repository into one field
issue.body: I don't see the need to have the user/organization and repository split out in to separate fields. So, I combined them... This also helps out with copy/pasting repositories from github, urls, etc.

issue.title: Where do you get these access_tokens?
issue.body:
I am building some github api based programs ( [star-history](https://github.com/timqian/star-history) ), and rate limit is a huge problem for me. I find you cleaverly solved the problem by using 6 different access_tokens.

I am wondering where do you get these tokens? Do you just sign up 6 account on github?

issue.title: Speed up force simulation when loading nodes
issue.body:
Currently it takes a while for nodes to settle when a repo is loaded, especially so for larger repos.
Speed up `force.tick()` simulation.
